# Terms & Conditions for Tenant SMS Alerts

**Program Name:** Tenant Automation Alerts by Jie Floyd Property Management

**Program Description:**  
This SMS service sends important property management notifications to tenants, including rent reminders, maintenance scheduling, lease renewal notices, payment confirmations, emergency alerts, and move-in/move-out instructions. Messages are only sent to current or prospective tenants who have explicitly opted in.

**Message Frequency:**  
Tenants can expect 0â€“4 messages per month on average, depending on account activity, maintenance needs, lease events, or emergencies. All messages are event-triggered and not promotional.

**Message & Data Rates Disclosure:**  
Message and data rates may apply according to your mobile carrier plan. Standard carrier charges apply.

**Support Contact Information:**  
For questions or assistance, reply **HELP**, or contact us at:  
Phone: +1 (582) 233-8696  
Email: jiefloyd@gmail.com  

**Opt-Out Instructions:**  
To stop receiving messages at any time, reply **STOP** to the number you received the message from.  
To get help, reply **HELP**.  
You may also contact us directly at the support info above.

